I've wanted this bag ever since I got into Brighton, which must be about ten years now.
I did a little dance.
(When no one could see me, I did a couple more little dances.
)  Savers in general can be really hit or miss - the clothing is fairly overpriced, but there are often deals to mitigate that.
Most locations have colored tags which denote what will be 50% off that day.
Thursdays, club card members get 20% off, and if you make a donation you also get 20% off.
But the bag is MINE!

