Went for a little school clothes shopping - prices are way out of whack - jeans with holes for $18, faded out t-shirts for $2, AND THEN... went to pay for 5 magazines.
A sign by the books clearly states: "Magazines 29 cents", only @ the checkout they were marked on the back 99 cents!!!
Talked to manager who just said that's their system.
Won't be going back.
Honesty is NOT company policy.

